<h1>BMI Calculator</h1>
<!-- 2) Introduction -->
<p>This professional BMI calculator helps adults estimate body fatness using height and weight, in either metric or US units. It instantly provides your BMI value, WHO category, BMI Prime, and your healthy weight range for your height.</p>
